OL,6,G     and Herzegovina
OL,7,     FSwitzerland v Bosnia and
OL,8,     FHerzegovina (Kick-off 8.00pm).
OL,9,     FLaura Woods presents coverage of
OL,10,     Fthe Group B match at Los Angeles
OL,11,     FStadium in Inglewood, USA. The
OL,12,     FSwiss won two of their three group
OL,13,     Fmatches in Qatar four years ago,
OL,14,     Fovercoming both Cameroon and
OL,15,     FSerbia as they finished second to
OL,16,     FBrazil on account of their loss to
OL,17,     Fthe South Americans, but they then
OL,18,     Fsuffered a heavy 6-1 loss to
OL,19,     FPortugal in the last-16. The
OL,20,     FBosnians failed to progress from
OL,21,     Fthe group stage at their only
OL,22,     Fprevious finals in Brazil in 2014,
