OL,5,G2230 FIFA World Cup 2026
OL,6,     FCanada v Qatar (Kick-off 11.00pm).
OL,7,     FLaura Woods presents coverage of
OL,8,     Fthe Group B match at BC Place
OL,9,     FVancouver in Canada. There has
OL,10,     Fonly ever been one previous
OL,11,     Fmeeting between these nations, a
OL,12,     F2022 friendly match in Vienna that
OL,13,     Fsaw just 150 people in attendance
OL,14,     Fas Canada claimed a 2-0 victory.
OL,15,     FThere will doubtless be many more
OL,16,     Fto witness tonight's clash in an
OL,17,     Farena that boasts a capacity in
OL,18,     Fexcess of 54,000, with the vast
OL,19,     Fmajority of those supporting the
OL,20,     Fco-hosts. Both teams are yet to
OL,21,     Fwin a match in the World Cup
OL,22,     Ffinals, but they avoided defeat in
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
