OL,6,G     Mother and Daughter Killers
OL,7,     FWith access to the victims'
OL,8,     Ffamilies, friends and the police,
OL,9,     Fthis documentary explores true
OL,10,     Fcrime cases linked to the social
OL,11,     Fmedia platform. In the early hours
OL,12,     Fof the 11th of February, 2022, two
OL,13,     F21-year-old men - Saqib Hussain
OL,14,     Fand Hashim Ijazuddin - were found
OL,15,     Fdead in a burning car on the A46
OL,16,     Fin Leicestershire. Police soon
OL,17,     Farrested two unlikely culprits -
OL,18,     F22-year-old TikTok influencer
OL,19,     FMahek Bukhari and her 45-year-old
OL,20,     Fmother Ansreen
